        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Photos of some collection sites: a - Thracian plain, Besaparski hills, near Ognyanovo vill. (habitat of Strongylognathus karawajewi); b - Stara planina, near Karnare vill. (habitat of S. karawajewi); c - Eastern Rhodopes, near Chernichino vill. (habitat of S. karawajewi and S. italicus); d - Eastern Rhodopes, near Gaberovo vill. (habitat of S. karawajewi and S. afer)." , "Figure 6. Strongylognathus italicus Finzi, 1924, workers: a - head, dorsal view; b - body, lateral view." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/513958" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/513965" .

